Orders - Class in org.example.model
Orders is the class used for modeling an order from the database.It mirrors a row from the orders table and has 3 constructors along with getters and setters needed in order to better manipulate our data.Note that the class is called "Orders" instead of "Order" because "order" is a reserved word in sql language
